=
Use the cross product to find the components of the unit vector $bh(n)$ perpendicular to the shaded plane in Fig.

#solution[
  Two of the plane vectors are $bold(v)_1 = [-1, 2, 0] "and " bold(v)_2 = [-1, 0, 3]$. $bold(v)_1 times bold(v)_2 = n = [6, 3, 2]$ and $|bold(n)| = 7$ gives $bh(n) = 1/7 [6, 3, 2]$
]